{"tid":334274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BBC公布高薪員工名單 性別歧視意外曝光","createTime":"2017-07-24T14:21:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T09:53:48.000Z","uid":1086,"like":4,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7c99716fb19d1453fccbd99a555c58da6a41b32d","tid":334274,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:21:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/07/19/realtime/3776582.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2Frealtime%2F3776582.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=8f7c1291&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司（BBC）19日在政府要求下，公布年薪逾15萬英鎊（約606萬新台幣）的96名高薪節目主持人薪資明細，結果意外讓性別薪資差異曝光，<span style=\"color: red;\">男性明星主持人的薪水竟比女性明星主持人的薪水高出5倍</span>。<br />\nBBC每周觸及95%的英國成人與全球3億7200萬觀眾，但國家公共媒體BBC也面臨當局嚴厲的財政檢查。<span style=\"color: red;\">BBC公開的清單中，其中三分之二男性與工作分量相當的女性薪資還高</span>。<br />\n<br />\nBBC最高薪的男主持人克里斯&middot;埃文斯（Chris Evans）在2016/17財政年度的薪水高達225萬英鎊，他主持熱門的晨間節目和早前的汽車節目「Top Gear」。薪水最高的BBC女主持人則是克勞蒂亞‧溫克曼（Claudia Winkleman），她的年薪不到一百萬英鎊。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司（BBC）今天首次被迫公布領取高薪人員名單，因男女薪資不平等遭砲轟。<br />\n<br />\n法新社及BBC報導，擁有94年歷史的BBC在去年修改章程後，今年首度被迫揭露2016至2017年賺進超過15萬英鎊（約台幣600萬）人員名單。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">這份名單上有超過200人，包括高層主管、演員、主持人、編劇和技術人員，但僅1/3是女性</span>。<br />\n<br />\nBBC總裁霍爾勛爵（Lord Hall）在聲明中為BBC辯護，表示BBC「比傳播同業和公部門更具多樣性」，但承認「需付出更多努力」。<br />\n<br />\n他表示：「我們已經為2020年設下清楚目標，那就是<span style=\"color: red;\">領導和主持角色男女要各占半數</span>。」<br />\n<br />\nSource<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6811/2593742?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6811%2F2593742%3Ffrom%3Dudn-catelistnews_ch2&d=786xU7PnK6mKZu4gmYOL3QHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=8c5318c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6811/2593742?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女權團體成功解決男女不平等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d15cb5ec6912b908792e83880f33318afabd87","tid":334274,"uid":46610,"like":47,"dislike":7,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:26:28.000Z","msg":"最憎女權用人工黎打飛機<br />\n如果女人人工低d點解唔請晒女人？<br />\n大家明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c85abbf62aa534ae9898d2b7dbacfea00b215d","tid":334274,"uid":7125,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:27:01.000Z","msg":"有無人有av男優同女優既收入資料？<br />\n要求同工同酬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4baa7abb7778e8d17cf30968444578b4d54904d","tid":334274,"uid":109077,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:30:21.000Z","msg":"公道講，如果職位一樣年資一樣，男女薪金差太遠真係有問題<br />\n但係要控制男女人數就有問題<br />\n頂你不如話護士男女要平均? 幼稚園老師男女要平均?<br />\n重點係，你冇能力就冇能力<br />\n如果女性真係咁有能力，個個做主持都得、個個做CEO都得啦下嘛<br />\n洗唔洗要SET個百分比「保障」女性? 咁其實咪都係歧視既一種"},{"pid":"cc80d7fe065b982d43bfba7fb1e89d96c657a6ba","tid":334274,"uid":57346,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:35:22.000Z","msg":"運動員/明星/高級管理人員點可以咁比較架！<br />\n不如話英國男足球員高薪過女足球員，所以要減佢地人工，減到同工同酬好未？大家都係踢九十分鐘，應該公平d！"},{"pid":"dbb212f09d67a3012d93b05abb31769d59081bb4","tid":334274,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:36:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"584890f0733ccd680f0ff6ac2394e87d657dbd99","tid":334274,"uid":66686,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T14:42:42.000Z","msg":"地盤工一個女都無又唔見女權要平權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"